# Backend lint and format

- **Lint and format are mandatory.** Before considering backend work done, run from `backend/`:
  - `npm run lint` — must exit with zero and report no errors or warnings.
  - `npm run format` — must pass (all files match Prettier style).
- **Fix before committing.** If either check fails, fix the issues (e.g. `npm run lint:fix`, `npm run format:fix`) so that `lint` and `format` both pass with no errors and no warnings.
- Do not introduce or leave ESLint errors/warnings or Prettier formatting violations in `backend/src/**/*.js`.
